<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5289975>
    dc:description "FIGURE 287. Neopicobia anthi (Fritsch) comb. nov., female (non-physogastric form). A, gnathosoma and propodonotum; B, coxal fields I and II; C, opisthosoma in ventral view; D, pygidial shield; E, peritremes; F, propodonotal setae si; G, hypostomal apex; H, claw pair of leg III; I, posterior part of movable cheliceral digit. Scale bars: A–D = 50 µm; E–I = 20 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5289975/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

